    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eva's Lab是一款由个人独立开发的第一人称益智解谜游戏。您将扮演在实验室中醒来的Eva，通过人工智能Omega的引导，利用手中的力场枪解决一个个谜题，离开实验室，获得自由，同时了解实验室的真实目的，以及Omega背后的故事。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法介绍:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家在关卡中获得力场枪，点击鼠标左键发射蓝色力场，蓝色力场从能量中心处发出斥力力场，可以使玩家跳得更高，也可以互动场景弹力球、激光等，打开开关或者通过障碍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >点击鼠标右键发射红色力场，红色力场从能量中心处发出吸力力场，可以吸引玩家或者场景弹力球、激光等，打开开关或者通过障碍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >力场枪可以通过清除键进行力场回收，重新发射获得更好的位置。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >蓝色斥力力场和红色引力力场</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292600/extras/abeeb22e8cd39ca4a0be6f48100c0fd1.poster.avif?t=1734054990\" width=536 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292600/extras/abeeb22e8cd39ca4a0be6f48100c0fd1.webm?t=1734054990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292600/extras/abeeb22e8cd39ca4a0be6f48100c0fd1.mp4?t=1734054990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292600/extras/eba5cb0d6df21f2039de645f6e67d014.poster.avif?t=1734054990\" width=536 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292600/extras/eba5cb0d6df21f2039de645f6e67d014.webm?t=1734054990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292600/extras/eba5cb0d6df21f2039de645f6e67d014.mp4?t=1734054990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >鼠标发射蓝色和红色力场</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292600/extras/59d5589dd62596501f797d1c77f69259.poster.avif?t=1734054990\" width=536 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292600/extras/59d5589dd62596501f797d1c77f69259.webm?t=1734054990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292600/extras/59d5589dd62596501f797d1c77f69259.mp4?t=1734054990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292600/extras/36748844fa0dc87d37081c6f7a6dd4f4.poster.avif?t=1734054990\" width=536 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292600/extras/36748844fa0dc87d37081c6f7a6dd4f4.webm?t=1734054990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292600/extras/36748844fa0dc87d37081c6f7a6dd4f4.mp4?t=1734054990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏关卡由浅入深，丰富的关卡供玩家挑战，需要玩家动脑思考，灵活使用力场枪，在合适的位置生成力场，解决谜题；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292600/extras/d62579509395ac681c2e3dfa3925ef6a.poster.avif?t=1734054990\" width=536 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292600/extras/d62579509395ac681c2e3dfa3925ef6a.webm?t=1734054990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292600/extras/d62579509395ac681c2e3dfa3925ef6a.mp4?t=1734054990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292600/extras/1774c74ed266593db47a6c6ddd476288.poster.avif?t=1734054990\" width=536 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292600/extras/1774c74ed266593db47a6c6ddd476288.webm?t=1734054990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292600/extras/1774c74ed266593db47a6c6ddd476288.mp4?t=1734054990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292600/extras/18a125bde5a97213bbecab705ee83eee.poster.avif?t=1734054990\" width=536 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292600/extras/18a125bde5a97213bbecab705ee83eee.webm?t=1734054990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292600/extras/18a125bde5a97213bbecab705ee83eee.mp4?t=1734054990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时可以寻找搜集要素，享受解谜的乐趣。</p>",
